{"tid":2276491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立黨全力支持侵侵留任美國總統","createTime":"2020-11-08T01:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T11:50:10.000Z","uid":254183,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da67a51c18d54800ee94453c2bef4f270950b522","tid":2276491,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/fully-support-donald-trump-continue-be-president\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Ffully-support-donald-trump-continue-be-president&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2ylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=01fd35cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/fully-support-donald-trump-continue-be-president</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我睇過最痴線嘅連署了，香港人公然干涉美國內政<br />\n最好笑嘅係連登仔當成寶嘅白宮連署網站，係由佢哋口中奶共總統奧巴馬設置<br />\n雖然侵侵上台後仲保留，事實上侵侵根本唔管呢玩意<br />\n所謂連署達標白宮需做出回應，到侵侵上任後也等同廢紙，根本冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31766980a94b27c8bd9dade237e5ef4a1ddd07e5","tid":2276491,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"香港人改變世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de76c1c28322b2006f4d2d13252bca9253fcdd8d","tid":2276491,"uid":105798,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:04:56.000Z","msg":"掛住香港個名就咪出醜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38da481c946bddf1bbbe8eaeca8ba58ffc6a7305","tid":2276491,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"de76c1c28322b2006f4d2d13252bca9253fcdd8d","tid":2276491,"uid":105798,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:04:56.000Z","msg":"掛住香港個名就咪出醜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re